(38, 4, '2012-11-30 15:14:26', '2012-11-30 14:14:26', '<div>\r\n<div><a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/membership/membership/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-39"><img class="wp-image-39 alignright" title="membership" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/membership.jpg" alt="We respect our women." width="268" height="201" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\nIf you want to have an awesome Frisbee experience, become a member of WAF! Fill in this form or contact the board by sending an <strong><a href="mailto:waf@wur.nl">email</a></strong>. The Thursday trainings are open for everyone who has a sports card, including employees of the WUR, Tuesday trainings are accessible for students only.\r\n\r\nThe yearly contribution of WAF is 25,-. WAF has several teams playing in competitions organized by the National Frisbee Federation throughout the year; Outdoor Open, Outdoor Mixed and Indoor competition. Joining one of these competitions costs an additional 12,<span style="font-size: small;">-</span>.\r\n\r\nIf you want to end your membership of WAF <strong><a title="Get in contact with the board!" href="emailto:waf@wur.nl">email</a> </strong>the board before the 31st of December. However, nobody can ever stop playing frisbee, youll be back!', 'Membership', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'membership', '', '', '2013-03-11 18:01:26', '2013-03-11 17:01:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=38', 0, 'page', '', 0),
