(87, 4, '2012-12-04 11:53:36', '2012-12-04 10:53:36', 'Because there was a lot of interest from non-students to participate in the WAF trainings, we agreed with the Bongerd that Thursday trainings are now also open for everybody with sports-rights of the Bongerd. In the old situation only students and PhD-students were able to join our trainings. The rules for the Tuesday trainings will remain the same, so Tuesday trainings are only open for students and PhD-students. Training locations and times are unchanged (Tuesday indoor at the Olympiahal and Thursday at the oudoor fields of the Bongerd).', 'Thursday trainings also open for non-students', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'thursday-trainings-also-open-for-non-students', '', '', '2012-12-04 11:53:36', '2012-12-04 10:53:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=87', 0, 'post', '', 0),
