(106, 4, '2012-12-09 17:47:54', '2012-12-09 16:47:54', 'We have two trainings a week; one training on Tuesday with Henri Veroude as our trainer and a training on Thursday with Bram te Brake as our occasional trainer. We play outdoor and indoor, so we also train outdoor and indoor. When the outdoor season changes into indoor and vice versa will be announced on this site. Keep an eye on the news!\r\n<h2><a name="TOC-Tuesday-training"></a><strong>Tuesday training<a href="http://localhost:8888/?attachment_id=34" rel="attachment wp-att-34"><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-34" title="practice" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/practice1.jpg" alt="" /></a></strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Outdoor season<strong>, </strong>20.00-21.30h, B-field@the Bongerd</li>\r\n	<li>Indoor season, 20.00-22.00h, @Olympia hal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCheck the local <a title="News!" href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/news/">news</a> to see whether we train indoor or outdoor.\r\n<h2><a name="TOC-Thursday-training"></a><strong>Thursday training</strong></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Entire year, 19.00h-19.30h, B-field@the Bongerd</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><a name="TOC-Locations-of-training"></a>Locations of training</h2>', 'Training', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '32-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-12-09 17:47:54', '2012-12-09 16:47:54', '', 32, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/32-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
