(123, 4, '2012-12-09 23:05:14', '2012-12-09 22:05:14', '<span style="font-size: small;">Welcome to the website of the Wageningen Allround Frisbee club, the place to be for lovers of flying plastic . Check our local news section for upcoming activities. Feel welcome to join our <a href="http://www.facebook.com/groups/167099670821/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">facebook</a> community for disc related discussions and other stuff. For more information on membership contact the <a href="mailto:waf@wur.nl">board</a>. We train twice a week and if you want to join, feel free to come. We train at Tuesday and at Thursday evening, you can find our training schedule <a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/training/">here</a>. We hope to see you at one of our trainings!<a href="http://localhost:8888/?attachment_id=95"><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-95" title="Practice" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/Isa_DSC004331-1024x329.jpg" alt="Going down" width="584" height="187" /></a></span>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-12-09 23:05:14', '2012-12-09 22:05:14', '', 4, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/4-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(125, 4, '2014-05-01 21:14:23', '2014-05-01 20:14:23', '&nbsp;\n\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/theboardz/999585_10202170488521932_1164802709_n/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-419"><img class="size-medium wp-image-419 alignright" title="The Board 2013-2014" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/999585_10202170488521932_1164802709_n-300x224.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="224" /></a>\n\nIn the complex world of bureaucracy our management strives to keep track of the administration and other boring stuff such as finances, tournament subscriptions and public relations so that you may fling circular plastics around without worrying. Nevertheless, we aim to act in the bests interests of our association.\n\nFor both interested people as well as members you can <strong><a title="WAF" href="mailto:waf@wur.nl">contact us</a></strong> to get information about the association, subscribe yourself to events or just to share something. We won''t bite. Much.\n<table width="251">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Karen van Engelshoven</td>\n<td><em>Chairman ;) </em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Kim R</td>\n<td><em>Treasurer</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Jasper Florijn</td>\n<td><em>Tournament &amp; Competition Director</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anton Bakker</td>\n<td><em>Secretary</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'The Board', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '25-autosave', '', '', '2014-05-01 21:14:23', '2014-05-01 20:14:23', '', 25, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/25-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
