(133, 4, '2012-11-30 15:14:26', '2012-11-30 14:14:26', 'The yearly contribution of WAF is 25,-. WAF has several teams playing in competitions organised by the National Frisbee Federation throughout the year; Outdoor Open, Outdoor Mixed <a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/membership/membership/" rel="attachment wp-att-39"><img class="alignright" title="membership" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/membership.jpg" alt="We respect our women." width="320" height="240" /></a>\r\n\r\nand Indoor competition. Joining one of these competitions costs an additional 12,50.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Yearly contribution 25</li>\r\n	<li>Per competition contribution 12,50</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2><a name="TOC-Termination-of-membership"></a>Termination of membership</h2>\r\nIf you want to end your membership of WAF, for whatever irrational reason, tell the board (waf@wur.nl) before the 31st of December. Otherwise you still have to pay the yearly contribution. However, nobody can ever stop playing frisbee, you''ll be back!', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '38-revision-11', '', '', '2012-11-30 15:14:26', '2012-11-30 14:14:26', '', 38, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/38-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(134, 4, '2013-03-11 17:54:04', '2013-03-11 16:54:04', '<div>If you want to have an awesome Frisbee experience, become a member of WAF! Fill in this form or contact the board by sending an <strong><a href="mailto:waf@wur.nl">email</a></strong>. The Thursday trainings are open for everyone who has a sports card, including employees of the WUR, Tuesday trainings are accessible for students only.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The yearly contribution of WAF is 25,-. WAF has several teams playing in competitions organized by the National Frisbee Federation throughout the year; Outdoor Open, Outdoor Mixed and Indoor competition. Joining one of these competitions costs an additional 12,<span style="font-size: small;">-</span>.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>If you want to end your membership of WAF <strong><a title="Get in contact with the board!" href="emailto:waf@wur.nl">email</a> </strong>the board before the 31st of December. However, nobody can ever stop playing frisbee, youll be back!</div>', 'Membership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '38-revision-12', '', '', '2013-03-11 17:54:04', '2013-03-11 16:54:04', '', 38, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/38-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
