(257, 4, '2013-03-21 18:13:52', '2013-03-21 17:13:52', 'It is finally time for the first activity of the activity committee of this year: the famous (flying?) pancake evening. The evening will be held on Wednesday the <strong>3th of April</strong> and will start at <strong>19.00h</strong> at Nieks place. We will bake pancakes with all kind of surprising toppings and we will finish with a matching dessert. The costs for the evening will not be much, but have to be decided upon still. You dont want to miss this unforgettable evening, so you can sign up at the <a title="Nomnomnom" href="https://www.facebook.com/events/153581054807662/" target="_blank">WAF facebook</a> page or let Imke, Mark or Henrieke know that you will come.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_182" align="aligncenter" width="300"]<a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/the-official-waf-pancake-evening/229585_10200150691024622_785920512_n/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-182"><img class="wp-image-182 " src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/229585_10200150691024622_785920512_n-300x294.jpg" alt="Mmm, pancakes." width="300" height="294" /></a> Catch it like a pancake[/caption]', 'The official WAF pancake evening', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '188-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-03-21 18:13:52', '2013-03-21 17:13:52', '', 188, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/188-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(258, 4, '2013-03-22 11:40:57', '2013-03-22 10:40:57', 'Next week''s Thursday there''s a special training with an external trainer. Leontine Sonneveldt, currently trainer at Airborn and the woman behind the national ladies training, will come to teach us some new tricks :) She''s an experienced trainer and as worked with both experienced and inexperienced players, so this is a perfect chance for everyone at WAF to learn something new and get some new feedback on your play.\r\n\r\nShe needs some input what to work on during the training, so please let me know (<a title="Email Bram" href="mailto:bramtebrake1@gmail.com">bramtebrake1@gmail.com</a>) if you have some ideas what to train (before Tuesday).\r\n\r\nI''ll talk to the soccer guys, and will ask for an extra half hour of playing time. After that, there are beers waiting for us at Djoeke''s party in Annie''s :)\r\n\r\nMake sure to be in time! Ready to start warming up at 19:00 sharp. So make sure to be there <strong>5 minutes in advance</strong>.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_202" align="alignleft" width="300"]<a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/thursday-training-with-leo-sonneveldt/527719_10151623758900676_2039113665_n/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-202"><img class="size-medium wp-image-202" title="Practice" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/527719_10151623758900676_2039113665_n-300x200.jpg" alt="Training" width="300" height="200" /></a> Practice with Leo[/caption]', 'Thursday training with Leo Sonneveldt', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '198-revision-4', '', '', '2013-03-22 11:40:57', '2013-03-22 10:40:57', '', 198, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/198-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
