(334, 4, '2013-04-11 16:30:24', '2013-04-11 15:30:24', '<a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/rising-high-sign-ups-1/rising-high/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-279"><img class=" wp-image-279 alignright" title="rising high" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/rising-high.jpg" alt="" width="120" height="120" /></a>\n\nHey WAFS!\n\nSome tournaments are on the horizon and we need to know if you want to join for that.\n<strong>Rising High (open team): 19+20 May\nGNSK (mixed): 8+9 June (National Student Championships)\n</strong>\n\nPlease fill in the forms in at the<a title="Subscription" href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/subscription/"> subscription page</a> if you want to join for Rising High or GNSK.\nLadies: you can contact Isa about joining the ladies team that will play at Rising High.\nRising High will be in Delft, costs are 40 eu. player fee + about 8 eu. teamfee.\nCamping is at the fields; it was a lot of fun last year with great food, party and weather.\nGNSK is only about 15 euro fee, and will take place in Nijmegen, together\nDon''t wait too long with signing up!\n\n&nbsp;', 'Rising High and GNSK Sign-ups!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '276-revision-14', '', '', '2013-04-11 16:30:24', '2013-04-11 15:30:24', '', 276, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/276-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
