(357, 4, '2013-04-23 08:17:58', '2013-04-23 07:17:58', 'For his thesis, Sander Piron is doing research about injuriesthat occur among Ultimate players. According to him a lot of players are under treatment for injuries but there is a lot unknown about the frequency of the different injuries. Therefore he opened a online survey to gain more insight into this topic. If you want to help him out, you can fill in his online survey you can find here<a title="https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/ultimatefrisbeevragenlijst" href="https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/ultimatefrisbeevragenlijst" target="_blank">https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/ultimatefrisbeevragenlijst</a>.\r\n\r\nIt takes about 4-8 minutes to fill in the survey and it is completely anonymous. You can fill in the survey until April 29.', 'Survey about Ultimate injuries', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'survey-about-ultimate-injuries', '', '', '2013-04-23 08:17:58', '2013-04-23 07:17:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=357', 0, 'post', '', 0),
