(420, 4, '2013-03-12 17:01:44', '2013-03-12 16:01:44', 'In the complex world of bureaucracy our management strives to keep track of the administration and other boring stuff such as finances, tournament subscriptions and public relations so that you may fling circular plastics around without worrying. Nevertheless, we aim to act in the bests interests of our association.\r\n\r\nFor both interested people as well as members you can <strong><a title="WAF" href="mailto:waf@wur.nl">contact us</a></strong> to get information about the association, subscribe yourself to events or just to share something. We won''t bite. Much.\r\n<table width="251">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Jasper Florijn</td>\r\n<td><em>President</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Jana Jilesen</td>\r\n<td><em>Treasurer</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Nick Verkade</td>\r\n<td><em>Tournament &amp; Competition Director</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Guido Breuer</td>\r\n<td><em>Secretary</em></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'The Board', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '25-revision-11', '', '', '2013-03-12 17:01:44', '2013-03-12 16:01:44', '', 25, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/25-revision-11/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
