(571, 4, '2014-05-11 22:54:15', '2014-05-11 21:54:15', '<a href="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/Intergalactic-poster.png"><img class="alignright wp-image-572 size-medium" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/Intergalactic-poster-207x300.png" alt="Intergalactic-poster" width="207" height="300" /></a>\r\n\r\n<em>Perhaps even more important than bringing a towel into the galaxy is to bring a disc because any (wo)man who has struggled against the length and breadth of the galaxy and still has a disc is clearly a person to be reckoned with.</em>\r\n\r\nOn the 22nd of May, WAF is organizing an introduction tournament from 18:45 - 21:30 for everybody who wants to get in touch with throwing unidentified flying objects across the air. Teams consist of at least 5 players, so drag all of your friends, family, random strangers to the artificial grass field at the Bongerd for an intergalactically awesome time!\r\n\r\nPlease register at<a class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/intergalactic">www.waf.wur.nl/index.php/intergalactic</a>! If you plan to bring in a team, but also when you decide to join individually as a Waffie. Joining individually is highly encouraged when you are not willing to admit to your friends that you are playing ultimate. Registering is not required though, so if you are not into commitment, just show up when you feel like it.\r\n\r\nDo not forget to share the poster on Facebook and/or instagram and/or whatever. You can download the high resolution poster by clicking on the image in this post (then just right click and choose "save as image" and Bob''s your uncle).\r\n\r\nWhat:          Ultimate Intergalactic Frisbee Experience\r\nWhen:            Thursday 22nd of May, 18:45  21:30\r\nWhere: Sports-centre de Bongerd [artificial grass field]\r\nFormat: 5 vs 5\r\nCosts: Free!\r\nWhat should I do:  Drag friends, family and housemates with you to form a team (and register your team <a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/intergalactic">here</a>)\r\n\r\nhttp://youtu.be/qORYO0atB6g', 'Ultimate Intergalactic Frisbee Experience', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ultimate-intergalactic-frisbee-experience', '', '', '2014-05-11 23:18:35', '2014-05-11 22:18:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=571', 0, 'post', '', 0),
