(603, 4, '2014-06-05 12:28:45', '2014-06-05 11:28:45', '<span style="color: #141823;">Love at First Flight (LAFF) is a tournament for starting teams/players and will start with a welcome party on Friday the 8th of August, running through the weekend with games on Saturday and Sunday (9&amp;10 August).</span><br style="color: #141823;" /><br style="color: #141823;" /><span style="color: #141823;">There will be an open, a mixed and a women division! We''ll play 5 vs 5 on lush fields of grass of 75m by 25m. Guys can have max 3 years of exper</span><span class="text_exposed_show" style="color: #141823;">ience. There is no restriction for female players.</span>\r\n\r\nPlayerfee: 40\r\nTeamfee: 100\r\n\r\nThe player fee includes a welcome drink at the welcome party on Friday evening, breakfast on Saturday and Sunday, a sandwich lunch on Saturday and Sunday, dinner on Saturday evening, 2 six-packs of water per team, and player gift.\r\n\r\nWe''re still looking for people to join us for this tournament! You can sign up at either on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/313928248757377/">facebook</a>or by sending an e-mail tothe board.\r\n\r\nFor more information, you can check out the LAFF <a href="http://laff.diabolicheaven.be/">website</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'WAF is going to Love at First Flight!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'waf-is-going-to-love-at-first-flight', '', '', '2014-10-14 17:17:58', '2014-10-14 17:17:58', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=603', 0, 'post', '', 0),
