(611, 4, '2014-06-05 21:28:39', '2014-06-05 20:28:39', '<span style="color: #141823;">Love at First Flight (LAFF) is a tournament for starting teams/players and will start with a welcome party on Friday the 8th of August, running through the weekend with games on Saturday and Sunday (9&amp;10 August).</span><br style="color: #141823;" /><br style="color: #141823;" /><span style="color: #141823;">There will be an open, a mixed and a women division! We''ll play 5 vs 5 on lush fields of grass of 75m by 25m. Guys can have max 3 years of exper</span><span class="text_exposed_show" style="color: #141823;">ience. There is no restriction for female players.</span>\r\n\r\nPlayerfee: 40\r\nTeamfee: 100\r\n\r\nThe player fee includes a welcome drink at the welcome party on Friday evening, breakfast on Saturday and Sunday, a sandwich lunch on Saturday and Sunday, dinner on Saturday evening, 2 six-packs of water per team, and player gift.\r\n\r\nWe''re still looking for people to join us for this tournament! You can sign up at either on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/313928248757377/">facebook</a>or by sending an <a href="waf@wur.nl">e-mail</a> tothe board.\r\n\r\nFor more information, you can check out the LAFF <a href="http://laff.diabolicheaven.be/">website</a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/10322449_10203222070409236_30052768233228990_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-604" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/10322449_10203222070409236_30052768233228990_n.jpg" alt="10322449_10203222070409236_30052768233228990_n" width="960" height="419" /></a>', 'WAF is going to Love at First Flight!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '603-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-05 21:28:39', '2014-06-05 20:28:39', '', 603, 'http://localhost:8888/index.php/603-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
