(1456, 4, '2013-03-26 02:19:04', '2013-03-26 01:19:04', '[caption id="attachment_182" align="alignright" width="300"]<a href="http://localhost:8888/index.php/the-official-waf-pancake-evening/229585_10200150691024622_785920512_n/#main" rel="attachment wp-att-182"><img class="wp-image-182 " src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/229585_10200150691024622_785920512_n-300x294.jpg" alt="Mmm, pancakes." width="300" height="294" /></a> Catch it like a pancake[/caption]It is finally time for the first activity of the activity committee of this year: the famous (flying?) pancake evening. The evening will be held on Wednesday the <strong>3th of April</strong> and will start at <strong>19.00h</strong> at Nieks place. We will bake pancakes with all kind of surprising toppings and we will finish with a matching dessert. The costs for the evening will not be much, but have to be decided upon still. You dont want to miss this unforgettable evening, so you can sign up at the <a title="Nomnomnom" href="https://www.facebook.com/events/153581054807662/" target="_blank">WAF facebook</a> page or let Imke, Mark or Henrieke know that you will come.\r\n\r\n', 'The official WAF pancake evening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '188-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-03-26 02:19:04', '2013-03-26 01:19:04', '', 188, 'http://localhost:8888/188-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1457, 4, '2015-04-02 14:19:59', '2015-04-02 14:19:59', '\r\n\r\nTomorrows practice will be Bring a Friend to Frisbee practice. If possible bring your BFF, otherwise consider bringing any other friend, neighbor, colleague, random stranger or pet. We will hire a bouncer to keep anyone off the field who did not bring anyone to the practice! Practice starts at 20.00h as usual.\r\n\r\nThis is also an excellent opportunity to get your team ready for Love at First Flight, our introduction tournament the 16th of April!', 'BFF Practice', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '266-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-02 14:19:59', '2015-04-02 14:19:59', '', 266, 'http://localhost:8888/266-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
